      "content": "i know i should talk to someone. i know the \"standard\" advice. but what's the point? the version of me that people respected, the one that actually mattered... that person is dead. there's no \"rebuilding\" from this. you can't rebuild a person once the foundation is just completely gone. it feels like a permanent end.",
